Philips has agreed to protect the privacy of your data consistent with the Philips ActiveLink Privacy Policy Our Website contains links to other websites not owned or operated by WeightWatchers.com , Inc. ( for example , if you " click " on a banner advertisement , you will likely be taken off our Website ) , including links to websites operated by franchisees of Weight Watchers International , Inc .
