Surveys , administered through SurveyMonkey , which are opt-in surveys inviting readers to submit their opinion .
Our Contact Us page does not ask for any personally identifiable information .
Sometimes , children write TeensHealth with a personal medical question .
As stated elsewhere , TeensHealth generally does not answer such questions and does not collect email addresses on the Contact Us form in order to be able to respond .
However , there are times when a visitor includes an email address and a physician believes it is advisable to ask a follow-up question or offer a comment , for instance , in the case of a life-threatening condition .
Only in these rare and serious instances will TeensHealth respond to an individual communication or take action on the information .
